    <item>
      <title>私人信贷吸引了1000亿美元的基金，因为通货膨胀率很高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/private-credit-lures-100-billion-fund-seeing-sticky-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Colonial First State 管理着价值 1,510 亿澳元（1,000 亿美元）的澳大利亚养老金和财富资产，由于预计利率将在较长时间内维持高位，该公司计划增加数十亿美元的私人信贷交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/private-credit-lures-100-billion-fund-seeing-sticky-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 21:24:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
