    <item>
      <title>巴西央行行长罗伯托·坎波斯·内托表示通胀预测将会改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/brazil-analysts-see-faster-inflation-into-2026-as-outlook-dims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行行长表示，消费者价格预测将有所改善，此前一项受到密切关注的调查显示，经济学家将 2024-2026 年通胀预期上调至进一步高于目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/brazil-analysts-see-faster-inflation-into-2026-as-outlook-dims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:57:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stellantis 为意大利提供另外两款车型以化解争议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/stellantis-may-make-two-more-cars-in-italy-to-defuse-output-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Stellantis NV 提议在意大利再生产两款混合动力汽车，这是其安抚当地政界人士的努力的一部分，因为这家菲亚特制造商希望将部分生产转移到成本较低的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/stellantis-may-make-two-more-cars-in-italy-to-defuse-output-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 10:57:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
